Subject: RE: [VB] Electrical mystery

Have your battery load tested. It could also be a bad connection is the
system and pass a small amount of power but not pass alot of current when
asked to. Clean all connections between the positive battery terminal and
fuse block, light switch and Ignition switch. Don't forget the negative
cable and trans to body bond strap.

Ted

