Need a little help with my electrical system. Its a 12 volt converted '65
Bus that has a dead electrical system. The battery checks out at 12 volts
and I have 12 volts going to the fuse box and to the headlight switch and to
the ignition switch. When I turn the key, the whole system loses voltage.
